scenes.description: Mori Calliope explores the 'Hell Temple' area in her 5th-anniversary virtual world.
Calliope discovers a giant skeleton hand and decides to stand on it for some poses.
Calliope interacts with her fans (deadbeats) and shows off her full-body tracking with various poses.
Calliope moves towards a dilapidated city area and finds a camera stand.
A cinematic camera sweep of the 'Dilapidated City' while Calliope provides commentary.
Calliope reveals a 'No Jacket' version of her outfit and prepares the audience for a new memory segment.
